Package islandtrader.core

Class RescuedSailor

java.lang.Object
islandtrader.core.Entity
islandtrader.core.RandomEvent
islandtrader.core.RescuedSailor
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class RescuedSailor
extends RandomEvent
Represents the RandomEvent "Rescued Sailors", when the Traders have this encounters they are rewarded with a monetary amount, that will vary depending on the number of Rescued Sailors they save.
Author:
Maria Heloisa Balzaretti
